  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1018">
<l>piṟarnāṇat takkatu tāṉāṇā ṉāyi</l>
<l>ṉaṟanāṇat takka tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Virtue is likely to forsake him who shamelessly does what others are ashamed of.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
